Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: NYC aid bill passed
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z98cm
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 14 Dec 1975
Filibuster bid fails to derail the NYC aid bill which is passed by both Houses. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less